{"tid":2409573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普人氣不減 二度彈劾無罪後首度露面 支持者包圍高喊USA","createTime":"2021-02-16T02:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T09:24:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":404,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0e501822f3904147baa8153a7b39b2f534d248","tid":2409573,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕被指控煽動1月6日的美國前總統川普，面臨二度彈劾，13日聯邦參議院裁定無罪，再次全身而退的川普，在當地時間15日首度現身，卸任後的川普人氣不減，大批支持者包圍高喊「USA」，川普也在車內笑著回應支持者比讚。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n打完高爾夫球的川普一現身立刻引發騷動，支持者高喊「USA」，在道路兩旁揮舞美國國旗、競選旗幟，川普在車內向支持者豎起大拇指。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n集會發起者稱，這次活動旨在支持「美國最偉大的總統」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440396&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=67a3c9fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440396&h=9e164e47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440396</a>"},{"pid":"edb7c9e4a9b21d730f3f59fde4d456cb2731801b","tid":2409573,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"></span>"},{"pid":"5b624662b91a3204bd6f486a580c4882138de79b","tid":2409573,"uid":127575,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac